<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.4.9">
<l>kaḷḷattēṉ poyyakattē ṉātalāl pōtorukāl kavalai yeṉṉum</l>
<l>veḷḷattēṟ keṉkolō viḷaivayaluṭ karunīlaṅ kaḷaiñar tāḷāl</l>
<l>taḷḷattēṉ maṇanāṟun taṇcēṟai yemperumāṉ tāḷai nāḷum</l>
<l>uḷḷattē vaippāruk kitukāṇī reṉṉuḷḷa muruku māṟē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I, a rogue, have a false heart; due to that, what [will happen] someday to me</l>
<l>[Sunk] in a flood called misery? See, this is the way that my heart melts</l>
<l>For those who daily keep in [their] hearts the feet</l>
<l rend="indent">of our great lord of cool Cēṟai</l>
<l>Where the scent of nectar wafts as laborers in the ripening fields</l>
<l rend="indent">jostle dark blue lilies with their feet.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
